{"tid":1537182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[百屌成才  菊花獻上] 勇武係時候休養一兩個星期，專注於國際文宣，然後再勇武過","createTime":"2019-09-03T23:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T01:46:17.000Z","uid":17510,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d393a081bbcc8b14cd5fa1ff854be085286eadac","tid":1537182,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:50:12.000Z","msg":"勇武左兩個月咁耐，其實我地儲落唔少料製造核彈<br />\n<br />\n我地而家應該休養生息兼專注國際文宣<br />\n<strong>重點</strong>有兩個<br />\n1.  希望G20會擺香港上枱<br />\n2. 促成美國通過人權法<br />\n<br />\n目的二達成之後先至再勇武，目的係希望美國引用人權法制裁港共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地既料有乜野？咪大把黑警暴虐鏡頭囉<br />\n係時候挑選精美鏡頭做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n休養唔代表放棄<br />\n期間如果有人試圖做大台、出賣香港，我地將會毫不猶疑地行出黎捍衛家園<br />\n<br />\n但係而家，我地有必要將我地既勇武成果展示於全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835cadcf66014276473a99b7bb70a1efbe6a8d62","tid":1537182,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61e51762cb29d6548345961af3cf356153c3b435","tid":1537182,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64bd8c8fca51c72d8f51daf31bbacc395f6300c","tid":1537182,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"835cadcf66014276473a99b7bb70a1efbe6a8d62","tid":1537182,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcp